{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and they found that they not only had one concentration camp, but about five concentration camps in Hannover.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Consequently, the book was written based on their findings, and major exhibits were had about it in Hannover, to educate the public about it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you were at the Continental Gummi-Werke scouting around, did you get to speak to anyone there?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, thank.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is where Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stuhlberg, Claus Stuhlberg comes in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, in the process of writing this book, several people, authors of the book, came and interviewed people who lived in these summer homes, where I thought-- that I thought I belonged to the SS when I was incarcerated, only to find that, no, they were residents.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they couldn't find anybody who remembered this period.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while we were walking there, I said, there are some people working in the yard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'd like to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, Gloria, you're wasting your time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We already thoroughly examined this before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, if you don't mind, I'd like to ask these people, and then I'll be satisfied.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it so happened that these-- the lady, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lena, said, well, you're very lucky, because we are the only ones left here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are the oldest residents of this area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And yes, we remember very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we-- [LAUGHS] she asked us in and we sat down and talked, but we couldn't film her, because it was already beyond dusk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she invited us to come the following day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came and we sat in her yard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she served us schnapps and cookies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I drank to a good neighbor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, she related to me the time of that period, when I was incarcerated at the Continental Gummi-Werke.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
